flowchart TD
    Idea[Core Idea & Requirements]
    S1[System Architecture & Environment Setup]
    S2[Database Schema & Migration]
    S3[Backend Models & Controllers]
    S4[Frontend Blade UI & Integration]
    S5[Authentication & Role Management]
    S6[System Validation & Debugging]
